{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 3006280, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "洞友们有什么想法与建议吗？", "timestamp": 1637563444, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006285, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实我觉得树洞还行", "timestamp": 1637563467, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006288, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "知网", "timestamp": 1637563475, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006301, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "想法：活跃度×严肃度＝常数\n建议：不要想", "timestamp": 1637563571, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006303, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "树洞虽然戾气重，但好歹能正常讨论。知乎删帖越来越厉害，甚至删帖都不会通知了", "timestamp": 1637563574, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006314, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "或许可以搞个类似CAP Theorem的，人气、言论自由、和谐三者只能最多选两个", "timestamp": 1637563632, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006335, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": 3006303, "tag": null, "text": "人多又要能尽量畅所欲言 => 必定会有意见很不一样的，常常看到反方意见就会火气大，言谈也会比较暴躁容易吵起来\n人多又要和谐 => 虚假的和平\n言论自由又要和谐 => 和自己相似度极高的小圈圈内的交友", "timestamp": 1637563779, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006396, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": 3006335, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 有道理", "timestamp": 1637564100, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006418, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": 3006335, "tag": null, "text": "其实我的想法是，互联网不应该像现在这样是一个死气沉沉却又充满对立被且被互联网巨头把控圈地的沼泽，而应该是一片吹着自由之风的绿茵", "timestamp": 1637564193, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006429, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": 3006335, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 赞同，活跃度和高质量不可能共存", "timestamp": 1637564246, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006436, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": 3006418, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 扼杀自由的就是自由本身", "timestamp": 1637564295, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006444, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": 3006418, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那确实是最初人们对互联网最美好的想象，或许很早很早、会上网的人还很少的时候是这样的", "timestamp": 1637564392, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3006459, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 569455, "reply_to": 3006444, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你说的有道理，或许最大的变量就是用户个数，也就是你说的“人气”", "timestamp": 1637564516, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 569455, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "树洞充满对立、知乎半死不活、闭社冷冷清清，在中文互联网中怎么才能打造出一款高质量的严肃交流社区呢？", "timestamp": 1637563417, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637564515, "url": "", "vote": {}}}